          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "CHSEP"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Targets were bombarded with helium ions and",
                "the fission fragment cross section yields, for the",
                "formation of the various fission fragments were",
                "determined radiochemically. After bombardment, the",
                "aluminum catcher foils and Re powder were dissolved",
                "in a solution of HCl-HNO3 and carders of the isotopes",
                "to be separated."
              ]
            }
          ],
