              },
              "free_text": [
                " Targets of enriched isotopes",
                "were prepared for bombardment in the form of a",
                "sandwich consisting of a thin layer of powder (of the",
                "order of 25 mg) between two zone refined hyper-pure",
                "aluminum foils. The aluminum foil also served as a",
                "catcher for all recoiling fission fragments escaping",
                "from the rhenium and was itself protected from",
                "external contamination by a second hyperpure aluminum",
                "foil."
